      ))}
    </section>

    <div class="author-bio">
      <h3>About {author}</h3>
      <p>Success Odyssey Hub explores the intersection of ancient philosophy, modern psychology, and practical strategy to help thoughtful people build lives of meaning, excellence, and lasting achievement. Our research draws from Stoic philosophy, behavioral economics, cognitive science, and the biographies of history's most accomplished individuals.</p>
    </div>

